data.description:
Welcome home! This bright and spacious home with two bedrooms downstairs is great for multigenerational living. The primary bedroom and bathroom are located on the first floor, together with another bedroom, full bath, living room, kitchen and breakfast area, as well as a dining room. Upstairs is a large loft, surrounded by three additional bedrooms and two full baths. The kitchen features a large island and lots of counter and cabinet space. The microwave also serves as a convection oven. A water softener and filter and a tankless water heater are only a few of the additional features. Enjoy entertaining in the multiple living areas and the back yard. The home has no neighbors behind! It overlooks a small green space.
The neighborhood is a short drive away from highways 183 and 183 A which offers quick access to every direction. It is also close to the metro rail, Northline, ACC campus, old town Leander, Smooth Village, Farmers Market, Leander Springs, The Forum Shopping Center and so much more!
